  "title": "Performing Artiste Manager",
  "description": "<p>Advocating for an artist's mental and physical health as needed.</p>\n<p>Negotiating contracts for local and foreign performing artists.</p>\n<p>Keep and update weekly routine performances.</p>\n<p>Handling interpersonal conflicts between artists, such as band members.</p>\n<p>Enforcing the terms of a contract.</p>\n<p>In charge of the admin of the performer including reporting to the management.</p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, public relations skills, marketing and advertising skills, negotiation skills, leadership skills and basic computer skills. Friendly, independent, aggressive, and has the ability to work as part of a team.</p>",
